{"ts":"2026-07-10T17:32:56.450Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-10T17:32:56.450Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-10T17:32:56.449Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Implementation slicing 2026-07-10 (grounded in current src state). Already public — do NOT redo: profile read-side (presets/plan/describe/lint exported via src/sdk/index.ts), schema runtime registries (resolveRuntimeFieldRegistry/resolveRuntimeStatusRegistry via src/sdk/runtime.ts), and generic PmClient.runTyped wrappers for the schema/config/profile/init actions. The actual gap: domain logic lives in CLI command modules — src/cli/commands/schema.ts (1973 lines), config.ts (1576), init.ts (955) + init-agent-guidance.ts (566), ~5.1k lines total — so SDK consumers reach these domains only through generic action dispatch, not typed primitives. Suggested slices: S1 schema mutation primitives (~150m) — extract add-type/add-field/status-def write paths into src/core/schema (fields-file/item-types-file/status-defs-file already own the file formats); command becomes parse+render. S2 config/settings primitives (~90m) — extract read/write/validate onto src/core/config/nested-settings; preserve the settings validator's unknown-key-stripping semantics (PR#314). S3 init + workspace-discovery primitive (~90m) — single source of truth for discovery; this is where the GH-501/pm-69nl class (init target invisible to discovery) gets fixed at the primitive level — coordinate with pm-69nl, do not duplicate its fix. S4 typed PmClient facades + SDK reference docs/tests (~60m) — replace generic payloads with typed inputs/outputs; each primitive must match the equivalent runAction result shape (semantics oracle, pm-usfg 07-06 note). Order: S1 first (schema gates the pm-w89s universality story); S2/S3 independent; S4 last."}]}],"before_hash":"e38cfeb29ad7683356d2b7d6e0c62718ef7be7de3db2acec744f90d0e92ce122","after_hash":"a557cfd5a6e7fb40685ce806b0a1483def5b9b12905eb060af76617617780cff"}
